      <title>美国人现在表示他们需要 150 万美元才能退休</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/saving-for-retirement-americans-say-they-need-1-5-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据西北互助银行 (Northwestern Mutual) 称，物价上涨和寿命延长导致美国成年人认为舒适的退休生活所需花费的费用激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/saving-for-retirement-americans-say-they-need-1-5-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 18:35:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
