      <title>随着投资组合转向盈利，乐高亿万富翁的现金储备不断增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/lego-billionaires-cash-pile-grows-as-portfolio-swings-to-profit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乐高帝国的亿万富翁所有者报告称，得益于投资组合的好转，利润增长了 5.9%。]]></description>
